Reference

Mapping

Functions for drawing maps based on Prague’s open geospatial data.

district_geofacet

Dataset to be used in the geofacet package

district_hexogram

Equal-area hexogram of Prague districts

district_names

Table of several variants of each districts names, with code

district_tilegram

Equal-area tilegram of Prague districts

prg_basemap()

Prague base maps for ggplot2

prg_endpoints

IPR Map Services

prg_tile()

Prague tiles for ggplot2 plots

Codes and metadata

Codes and metadata describing Prague of identifying Prague and related entities in various datasets.

Prague bbox in EPSG 5514 (Krovak)

prg_lau1

Prague LAU1 code

prg_metro_oecd

Prague code in OECD CITIES database of data on Functional Urban Areas

prg_nuts2

Prague NUTS2 code

prg_nuts3

Prague NUTS3 code

prg_okres

Prague 'okres' code

prg_okres_nuts

Prague 'okres LAU' code
